Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class ContactItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<ContactItem>
        • ohos.data.search.schema.ContactItem

  • public final class ContactItem
extends Schema<ContactItem>
    Represents the index schema for contact items.

    This schema is used to create indexes for contact items. It supports index fields phone, email, birthDate, gender, address, workLocation, and all the fields in CommonItem. Among these fields, identifier is mandatory and can be set via the CommonItem#setIdentifier(String) method.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
